dismissalText.commentary: Shan Masood lbw b Mehidy Hasan Miraz 57 (69b 2x4 0x6 139m) SR: 82.6

dismissalComment.html: Good length ball with hint of turn on the pitch, Masood misses the line of the ball as he tries to nudge it to the onside across the line, hits the front pad. Loud appeal from the bowler and the umpire raises his finger. Masood opts to review the decision, no bat involved, pitching and impact in line, hitting the middle-leg stump. Pakistan loses both their skipper and their first review.
